@startuml
actor Librarian
participant MainController
participant LibraryService
participant NotificationService
database MySQL
Librarian -> MainController: choose member and book
MainController -> LibraryService: borrowBook(book, member)
LibraryService -> LibraryService: validate limit, duplicates, availability
LibraryService -> MySQL: persist borrowing (JDBC DAO in database mode)
LibraryService --> MainController: Borrowing
MainController -> NotificationService: notify member
MainController --> Librarian: success toast
@enduml
